<DocsLayout title="§13 Telemetry Streaming" description="RCAN §13 — Telemetry Streaming. Robots publish continuous telemetry via the STREAM message type. This section defines the telemetry field registry, subscription model, sampling intervals, backpressure handling rules, and the schemas for battery, pose, velocity, and custom telemetry payloads.">
